telnet localhost 11211
set <key> <flag> <expires> <bytes>
*set sunqi 0 0 4
*1024
STORED
*incr sunqi 1
1025
*get sunqi
VALUE sunqi 0 4
1025
END
delete sunqi
DELETED
get sunqi
END
*set sunqi 0 0 4
*abcd
*append sunqi 0 0 4
*efgh
STORED
flush_all
quit

